        "timestamp": "2019-04-24 14:15:36.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI have a rebase conflict with current master due to https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/84523/4/packages/policy-xacmlpdp-docker/src/main/docker/Dockerfile@a12 changes.\nI wonder if creating /opt/app/policy/pdbx/etc/ssl is correct? Previously all images used to use /opt/app/policy/etc/ssl \n$POLICY_HOME set to /opt/app/policy/ in common-image and every app has it's own dir under $POLICY_HOME. I'm not sure should I keep my changes or adopt yours?",
        "patchset_number": 1
